nches, changes, commits, or pull\n   717\trequests.\n   718\t\n   719\t## Persist Or Recompute\n   720\t\n   721\tThe capture turn layer could be stored directly, or some of it could be\n   722\trecomputed from existing records and Git state.\n   723\t\n   724\tReasons to persist capture turns:\n   725\t\n","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-20T14:51:42.780Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]"}}}